title: Ebro In The Morning - "Eff It, We Fightin" + Gunna Denied Bail
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 5/23/2022.

Ebro, Rosenberg, Laura Stylez and the crew are in the studio breaking down the fight between two heroes at the Newark Airport, opening up the phone lines for "Eff It, We Fighting" and Gunna being denied bail.
